data.description: Just a quick drive from Shaw Air Force Base, this house has all that you need. Not only is it affordable, but it is updated and completely move in ready. It has a private backyard that is fully fenced in, two living rooms, and a super spacious primary bedroom! This home will surprise you with how much space there is. The second living room is huge with beautifully classic built ins. The screened in back patio & covered garage space are cherries on top! This home would be the perfect place to enjoy summers and fall nights! Come view this home today!! No HOA!
